<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,151,464]" pageId="11" pageNumber="462">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,548,367,392]" pageId="11" pageNumber="462">Flight period in South Korea.</emphasis>
Female: July. Males have not been recorded from South Korea. In Japan, males are collected from August to October (Murao 2014).
</paragraph>
